              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37676900/" class="">第49页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/141187109/" class=" " title="阿亮winner">阿亮winner</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37676900">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37676900/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p37676900-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class="">英国人太恶心，这些国家是造成中东今日局面的罪魁祸首

</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-04-29 17:03</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
